text.sentence: Hey Jack - I'm assuming you don't know the last name, but I'm betting you haven't known alot of other Tori's in your lifetime.
Anyway, I've been feeling nostalgic lately, so, I thought I would see what was up in your life.
I got married about 6 years ago, and I live with my husband, Pat, out in Katy.
I'm working at Enron downtown, doing commodity trading.
We're expecting a little girl in June, our first baby.
Anyway, I'd love to see what's going on with you.
